From 19f1d119016079f27223946378c56391d8121688 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 17:27:25 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Implement complete UBF Grants Intelligence Platform

All source files were empty shells. This commit builds the full application:

- lib/constants.js: TEAM, THEMES, PROGRAM_WINDOWS, KBAS, STATUSES, agent system prompt
- lib/helpers.js: daysLeft, formatDate, urgency/status/priority colours, formatCurrency
- lib/logo_b64.js: placeholder export
- hooks/useGrants.js: localStorage-backed grant state (add/update/delete)
- hooks/useAgent.js: Anthropic streaming API integration with abort support
- components/Sidebar.jsx: fixed nav sidebar with urgent badge
- components/Notification.jsx: animated toast notifications
- pages/LoginPage.jsx: team member selector login
- pages/Dashboard.jsx: KPI cards, upcoming deadlines, status breakdown, high-priority alerts
- pages/GrantTracker.jsx: full CRUD table with search/filter/sort and detail/edit views
- pages/AgentPage.jsx: Claude-powered chat with API key management and suggested prompts
- pages/PipelinePage.jsx: deadline-banded kanban view with pipeline value summary
- pages/TeamPage.jsx: per-member workload cards with urgent deadline warnings
- pages/UserGuide.jsx: sectioned staff guide with sidebar navigation

Build verified: vite build passes cleanly (197 kB JS bundle).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
